message.content:
1. Scanning times were longer for examinations performed on the open MR scanner.
2. The mean scanning time for examinations performed on the open MR scanner was 32 minutes.
3. The standard deviation of scanning times for examinations performed on the open MR scanner was 22 minutes.
4. The mean scanning time for examinations not performed on the open MR scanner was 20 minutes.
5. The standard deviation of scanning times for examinations not performed on the open MR scanner was 9 minutes.
6. The difference in scanning times between the open MR scanner and other scanners was statistically significant (P<0.0001).
